description: A mixed use development. Demolition of existing buildings. Construction of two buildings ( Building A 5-7 storey, Building B 4-8 storey) to provide 183 residential units (64x1 bed, 96x2 bed, 23x3 bed)478 sqm retail space for use class (A1/A2/A3/A4/A5/B1/D1/D2). Provision of car parking, cycle, storage area, pedestrian/ cycle route, landscaping and amenity space.
